[[File:Chisel detail.png|left|120px]]
A '''Chisel''' is a tool mainly used in the [[Crafting]] [[skill]] to cut and shape hard non-metals, mainly [[gem]]s and [[limestone]]. Chisels are also used in [[Fletching]] to cut gems into [[Gem bolt tips|bolt tips]]. Chisels are sold for the price of 1 coin at all [[general store]]s, except in [[Dorgesh-Kaan]] and [[East Ardougne|East]]/[[West Ardougne]]. There is a free chisel spawn in the [[Crafting Guild]], in [[Wizard Cromperty]]'s house in north-east East Ardougne, and one at the [[dense essence mine]]. At 15 [[Construction]], [[members]] can make a '''[[Tool store 1]]''' for the workshop room of their house; this tool store provides an unlimited supply of chisels.

